    "passive": {
      "name": "Tiger Pace",
      "description": "Enemy heroes hit by Wanwan's attacks will have their weakness exposed and position revealed for 5s. When hitting an enemy's weakness, Wanwan deals 67(+3*Hero Level) extra (True Damage) and increases their damage taken from her subsequent attacks by 10% for 5s. Wanwan can dash a short distance after each arrow fired from her Basic Attack. The dash speed scales with her Attack Speed. Wanwan's Basic Attack deals ( +100% Total Physical Attack) Physical Damage.",
